                <fr:title text="\neg  preserves the property"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\neg ]]></fr:tex> preserves the property</fr:title>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let's start with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\neg ]]></fr:tex> again.
Here are the strong Kleene and Dunn-Belnap tables for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\neg ]]></fr:tex>:</html:p>
                <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
                  <fr:frontmatter>
                    <fr:authors>
                      <fr:author>
