                  </fr:mainmatter>
                </fr:tree>
                <html:p>We want to show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\rightarrow ]]></fr:tex> preserves the <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {*}} / \mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex> property, that whenever both <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> have the property, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A \rightarrow  B]]></fr:tex> has it as well.
But if indeed both <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> have the property, then we know that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u(A)]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u(B)]]></fr:tex> can't be <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {N}}]]></fr:tex>, so we can set aside those rows and columns of the Dunn-Belnap table:</html:p>
                <html:table style="border-collapse: collapse;">
  <html:thead><html:tr>
    <html:td class="topedge leftedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\rightarrow ]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    <html:td class="topedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {T}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    <html:td class="topedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    <html:td class="topedge fade"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {N}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    <html:td class="topedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {F}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
  </html:tr></html:thead>
  <html:tbody>
    <html:tr>
      <html:td class="leftedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {T}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {T}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td class="fade"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {N}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {F}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    </html:tr>
    <html:tr>
      <html:td class="leftedge"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {T}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td class="fade"><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {T}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
      <html:td><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathsf {\mathbf {B}}]]></fr:tex></html:td>
    </html:tr>
